Place bagels on an ungreased baking sheet; spread with cream cheese. Set aside. In a large skillet over medium heat, cook and stir beef in oil for 3-5 minutes or until no longer pink. Season with salt and pepper. Using a slotted spoon, place beef on bagels. Top with tomato and mozzarella cheese. Broil 8 in. from the heat for 3-5 minutes or until cheese is melted and lightly browned.